name: Fuzz and Rocket
description: Fuzz and Rocket is an immersive 2D action platformer which incorporates both substance and style. It is centred around the main character, Fuzz and his sidekick, Rocket as they try to restore order to the land of Fulu. Mysterious masks have possessed the rulers of the 8 kingdoms of Fulu causing them to make life difficult for their subjects. It is up to Fuzz and Rocket to figure out what’s going on and trace the masks back to their source! Many challenges and obstacles stand in their way.

name: Star Fox
description: When Star Fox: Assault was announced, Nintendo also announced the development of a Star Fox arcade game. Unfortunately, nothing was heard about the project since and it has been assumed that the game was scrapped. As further proof that the game has been discontinued, nothing of the sort was unveiled at Nintendo's 2014 E3 presentation, where Star Fox Zero was announced, marking the eighth year of silence about the game.

Likin Hero is the first ever cartoon hero linking game!
Extraordinary graphic design & sound effect, 100 game levels and stimulating sound effects make you just can't stop playing it!
What are you still waiting for?! Download the game & join us in Likin Hero!

name: Sugary Delight
description: Pick the right ingredients , decorations and deliver on time. Make cute, colorful and delicious confectionaries and gain likes. Share your love for sweets with everyone and enjoy a sweet time.

name: Merge 3 Mania
description:
Don’t judge the game by its name! It is not just-another-ordinary-match-3-game. It is Merge-3 Maaania - the most intriguing and innovative combination of merge-3 and building construction, providing you with an irresistible puzzle solving experience.
M3M is an easy-to-pick-up but hard-to-master puzzle solver where you need to combine three or more pieces of the same element to create a more advanced element: from grasses to shrubs then trees, or cottages to tents then yurts. Instead of eliminating game-pieces, you create an ever-advancing township of prosperity and happiness.
Plan and strategise every step to build advanced elements like the Palace, Pyramid, and the Tower of Light; or even reach the ultimate Wonder of the ancients. See how far can you go before you run out of space.

name: Offshore Racing
description: Drive high speed motor boat in sea traffic along with police, pirates and golden boats. Be cautious of police patrols don’t crash into them. Collects coins by chasing and driving boat from sea traffic. Use rockets to destroy all pirates boats on you way.

name: Bowling Islands
description:
Have you ever played bowling at tropical islands? Well, now you can!
There are various and strange types of lanes, balls, and pins in this game.
Pull the throwing cursor to aim, and flick the ball to curve!
Let's become a Island Bowl Master!!

name: Mythic Mountain
description: An arcade-style snowboarding game where you play as mythical creatures escaping a crazed trapper (who really, really wants to sell you to black-market cryptozoologists).

name: New Star Cricket
description:
A big welcome from New Star Games as we expand the BAFTA award-winning gameplay of New Star Soccer into a whole new sporting arena!
In New Star Cricket, you are the star of the show, launching your cricket career as a promising young academy player. Build your skills, purchase all the trappings of a professional cricket player and rise to the pinnacle of the sport, playing in competitions all over the world!
As your career progresses, you must manage your relationships, keeping team-mates, the coach, your partner and your sponsors happy as you face dilemmas and exciting twists along the way.
Experience life as a professional cricketer, play for your national team and revel in the authenticity of a mobile cricket title that captures the spirit, skills, excitement and teams from the many cricket leagues around the world!
Equally enjoyable as a snack game for a few minutes or an intensive few hours, New Star Cricket will leave you entertained, amused and hungry for more, and it’s entirely free to play without any restriction!
What are you waiting for? This huge, detailed cricket universe is yours to own. So get your bat and ball and earn your first contract!

name: Pelé: Soccer Legend
description:
The official soccer game featuring greatest footballer Pelé.
Pelé: Soccer Legend is a new soccer experience with streamlined gesture controls, featuring the legend himself! Follow in Pelé’s footsteps in career mode and work your way from the backstreets of Brazil all the way up to become world champion

name: Pit Stop Racing: Manager
description:
[Pit Stop Racing: Manager] is based on the NASCAR car competition, and you can enjoy the fun of growing your character and gaining victory in the competition.
The NASCAR car competition is a popular sport that ranks the second place in the sports rankings in the United States. Train various cars and crew teams to win the official tournament.

name: Neon Man
description:
This will be a wonderful experience!
This is a very dynamic and addictive Game!
Swipe fingers to jump the floors and slide forward!!
Avoid Rotating-Obstacles!
Acquire Items (the Stars, Shields, Lightnings and Batteries) to survive!
Charge the Battery of the Neon Man to increase the speed!
A scary Circular-Saw chases the Neon Man.
Neon Man must escape away from the scary Circular-Saw!

name: Endless Drive
description: Endless truly procedural roads across different biomes and beautiful scenarios to experience the joy of driving.

name: Racing Rush
description:
One of the best simple and fun racing game for everyone.
You have problems with the hard control or get bored of difficult levels in other current racing game? Racing Rush is what you looking for. Control your car wheel and see how it passes other cars and collects energy as well as super items on the road.
Racing Rush is a high score game. The more cars you can pass, the more score you can get. However, be careful of crashing other cars if you don’t want to lose your fuel and continue your journey.
Do you think racing in the straight line is easy? Keep balance by careful control of car wheel and accelerate your speed by using bonus item.

name: Highway Cleaner
description:
You have to clean the highway so that cars can run.
Be careful not to let cars hit obstacles on the road.
To play the game, tap anywhere on the screen and drag the sweeper left or right to clear the obstacle.

name: Bicycle Tour
description:
Swipe to cycling through the beautiful sightseeing in France. Dive in the countryside melodies while dashing out all your opponents!!!
Reaching the cross line is one thing, you are expected to show your timing skill to crush other bicycles on the way.

name: Ramped Up!
description: Get ready for some pure bouncing action, satisfaction guaranteed!

name: CMYP
description:
Tap the cube carefully through each color pie obstacle and your cube will cross color with some color pinwheel!
You must follow the color pattern on each obstacle to cross it!​
The cube will switch colors when passing through the Color Pinwheel.
Be careful not to pass through the wrong color, or you’ll have to start again.

name: London Rush
description: Your car will respond to your command, but the night is dark and the street is full of obstacles, so be careful. If you fall, get up and try again, because every game is unique, and you'll notice to starting improving quickly! In the shop you can trade bulbs obtained from lamps, for a lot of upgrades to your car.

name: Nuclear Outrun
description:
Through some unforeseen (yet totally avoidable) world crisis, a nuclear missile is crashing down to ruin everyone's party. Drive & shoot your way out of a zombie-infested city as far as you can, before everything goes kaboom!
Collect survivors such as Pirates, Mimes, and Hipsters, each with their own special abilities. Mow down zombies with wacky weapons such as the Shark Gun, Fart Bazooka, and the Twitgun that shoots out #hashtag spewing birds.
When all else fails, launch Weapons of Mass Destruction like George the cyborg T-Rex!

name: Super Mega Lucky Box
description: In this spectacular game of colossal fun, reveal numbers one-by-one and close a corresponding square on one of your cards. Your goal is to score as many points as possible, and you'll do that mostly by crossing off the nine numbers printed in a 3x3 grid.

name: Agent from C.O.G.O.O.
description: From the creators of World of Mines, The Agents from C.O.G.O.O is another classic, throwback PC puzzle game with a World Map twist with addictive game play. Inspired by the original game written for many computing platforms since the 1960s.

name: Worm AR
description: Move the worm through the sand box using the 2 control buttons. Navigate to the fruits. Do not move onto the walls and do not bite the worm itself! Watch the time!

name: Hopper Cat
description: Join the addiction with the amazing hopper cat!

name: Zac's Batting Academy
description: Take control of Zac as he progresses through various stages, facing an increasingly challenging array of bowling machines as he blocks, sweeps and smashes his way to victory. Unlock awesome upgrades as you advance and see how many official player cards you can collect along the way. Hours of fun await as you take on the challenge to see if you can become the next master batsman.

name: Tetroon
description:
Are you a fan of classic puzzle games, such as Tetris, Bejeweled, or Dr. Mario?
Tetroon is the next evolution in puzzle games. Take to the skies with your fleets of tetroons (science balloons), where you will maneuver your fleets to complete the objectives for the selected game mode.
Tetroon is currently available with two game modes: Marathon and Countdown.
In Marathon mode, endless fleets of tetroons are yours to command. Maneuver your fleets with the goal of completing rows of tetroons, earning you points. The more rows completed, the higher the score. And, as the game advances, so do both the difficulty and the scores. Boasting of 26 unique fleet formations, the challenges are unlike any you have ever seen before!
In Countdown mode, you experience all the same great gameplay as in Marathon, but with the ultimate goal of completing a fixed number of lines. As an added challenge, you can choose a starting height in combination with a level, earning an additional score multiplier for each line completed.
Good Luck!

name: Venus Flytraps
description:
Let's grow a cute carnivorous plant!
Simulation game "Flytrap" is a game that you grow it to eat the insects to Dionaea muscipula.
I eat Flycatcher may extend when you tap the stage.
To fit the timing in insects to move, so you Saseyo eat!
I grow more and more Dionaea muscipula eat lots of insects.
Would to any growth?

name: Kori DRoP
description:
Tap to pop the blocks.
Save the little dude from the water.
Eat lots of carrots.
81 levels of fun and frustration.

name: Kakikuku Jump!
description:
Enjoy jumping games for free.
Overcome your obstacles by jumping in time.
You can collect a variety of jumpers with unique coins earned during play.
It`s difficult, but you can do it. Never give up!

name: Goodnight Rudy
description:
Match three of the same tiles. Vertically, horizontally or by a right angle. Doesn’t matter! As long as there are three of a kind. The tiles disappear as you match them.
Set the tiles on the grid as you wish.

Good night Rudy. Sleep tight, don’t let the bed bugs bite.
Simple, but Addictive.

name: Smart Cookie Cat
description: Developed by Ouat Entertainment, this puzzle game puts your logical thinking and observation skills to the test!

name: Tiny World
description:
Tiny World: the latest competitive strategy game!
A competitive strategy game set on the most smallest of floating islands, remains from a place where peace and prosperity were fact - until two greedy sons lost their senses after their father passed away.
This is the beginning of an epic battle for the remaining lands. Who will get the most land? Who gets the most Victory Points? Who is the most strategic one? Is it you?

name: Hacker the Beginning
description:
A story full of adventure and action awaits you.
Prove that you are a real hacker. Break through firewalls, infiltrate systems and complete missions.
Discover the vulnerabilities of the digital world. Prove that all systems are unreliable by exploiting the weaknesses of technology. Your goal is to find vulnerabilities in systems, crack passwords, hack into networks, steal data and use it to discover important information to reach the end of the story.
Are you ready to feel like a real hacker with the game's amazing scenario and comic book style cutscenes! Follow the events that happen to three friends. Remember. There is a reason for every mission and we will bring justice.
Hacker Prologue is the perfect choice for players interested in the mysterious world of hackers and digital systems.

name: Z.O.N.A Project X
description:
Z.O.N.A Project X - first person shooter based in a post-apocalyptic world.
Action of the game takes place in a near future time, where almost all of mankind was destroyed with the nuclear weapon's. The earth became unsuitable for normal existence. Only one group of survivor's fight to survive in this hostile and dangerous world and you are one of them! The future of all the mankind depends on you, are you up for the challenge?
Unpredictable plot, great graphics with lots of different of weapons, Bloodthirsty monsters and greedy thugs - this is what awaits you in the Z.O.N.A Project X!

name: Stratoskirmish
description: Stratoskirmish is a historical-fiction action-combat vertical shooting game currently in development.

name: New Rule: The Game is...
description: Kill cybernetically enhanced bugs in this 3D top-down voxel shooter. Twist: the rules change every 15 secs and the level is changing constantly. So level up your skills to stay ahead of leveling enemies!

name: Dungeon Shooter: Dark Temple
description: A retro style FPS & RPG game.

name: Human Save Plan
description: This is a kind of dark RPG treasure brushing game. The affixes of props are randomly generated and can be exchanged at will. With the addition of the thinking system, players can make objects carry out specific AI logic through thinking output.

name: Seroutte
description: Seroutte is a short atmospheric experimental horror dreamscape based on the developer's nightmares. It explores themes such as the loss of control, fear of the dark, and the paranoia found within the unknown.

name: Polar Bear Game
description: The arctic is a big place. Ever wanted to explore the endless expanses of the arctic as a Polar Bear? Well now you can in Polar Bear Game. Explore and survive a procedurally generated, infinite world, where, as a polar bear, you can choose whatever you want to do!

name: Garfield
description: Garfield is an unfinished video game that was developed for the Atari 2600. The game was never officially released due to the videogame crash of 1983, which resulted in the cancellation of many other games that were being produced by Atari, including another Garfield title. It is based on the popular comic strip of the same name.

name: Pokémon Coral Version
description:
Welcome to the Onwa Region, a region far away from Kanto and Johto. Onwa is the setting for Pokémon Coral Version, a romhack that sets out to recreate the feeling of playing Pokémon Gold, Silver, and Crystal for the first time. Journey through Onwa meeting interesting characters, earning the 8 Onwa League Badges, and working your way towards challenging the Onwa Pokémon League.

Pokémon Coral Version features a simple story akin to the first two generations of Pokémon with many interesting characters and locations to see along the way. Things aren't completely what they seem, however. There has been talk of a group of ruffians abusing Pokémon and using them in their money-making schemes. That can't be good news...

The 2022 Demo has been rebuilt from the ground up in the Pokémon Polished Crystal engine allowing for many new features such as 60fps gameplay, abilities, and many many more. Much of the game design has been tweaked or completely overhauled, so even if you've played older demos, you should be in for a new and exciting experience!

description: Riboud and Fairies is an excellent horizontal board game for beautiful girls, similar to Super Mario. It has extremely exquisite dynamic beauty CG. You can use your fighting skills to clear the bound objects on the beauty! Its level design is also very creative, and the dialogue is also very funny.

Have you ever tried to find beautiful constellations in the vast sky? Swipe finger, link the stars … find the mystery answers in this unique and innovative puzzle game.
Connecting shining stars to get beautiful constellations.
Let's start a wonderful journey into the sky.

Just click the chessboard to gain high score!

Cross the roadblock, find the road, help the little chick seek its own lover, maybe it is a exploring road, when he find, the two will be made one, it's so funny.

name: MLB Home Run Derby 2022
description: MLB Home Run Derby brings the non-stop action of the Home Run Derby to you. Do you have the skill to be a Home Run Derby Champion? With three distinct game modes, 100+ batters to collect, and constant live events - there is always a reason to swing for the fences in MLB Home Run Derby!

name: Party Wave
description:
An Action Surfing Game Developed by Mistwalker.
Total of 50 stages! Don't forget the additional bonus stages and Arcade Mode, too.
There are two elements in playing Party Wave: paddling and surfing. For paddling, touch surfers and drag them to a spot where the surf breaks, while avoiding the obstacles such as dolphins and turtles. And for surfing, touch surfers to make them turn and jump to prevent wipeouts.
Let's surf a wave with the surfing crowd and the board-riding dog, Skip, while getting help from three mermaid sisters and Hiso Alien, who provides valuable bonuses.
Party Wave!

description: Challenge your friends to a game of Super Rad Ball, the fast-paced multiplayer sport of the future.​

name: Mini Golf Battle
description: Challenge your friends to a fun-filled match of Mini Golf Battle on iMessage. Experience the innovative multiplayer strike-by-strike gameplay where players interact with each other on the course. Knock, bump and block your opponent's ball in epic battles to find out who is the Minigolf champion!

name: EarthGang: Mirrorland
description: Join EarthGang (Olu & Wowgr8) as they fight their way along the red- brick road from Rags to Royalty, all the way to Mirrorland.

name: Concert Kings: Music Tycoon
description: Tap and swipe to rake in the royalties in Concert Kings Idle Music Tycoon, a rock ‘n roll idle clicker! Become a pro band manager and build a sprawling music empire in this rockin’ tapper game. Collect music notes to earn riches, then spend ‘em on epic upgrades. You’ll even earn cash while you’re away! Buy a better stage, play bigger venues, recruit new talent, jam to original rock & pop music, and impress influencers on your journey to fame and fortune.

name: Beezaster
description: Build an army and coordinate the defence of your Hive while at the same time attempting to capture the enemy Hives you discover as you complete a variety of unique missions. Fast paced, fun, action packed adventure.

name: Transformers Bumblebee
description: The buzz is building for Bumblebee to save the world! Embark on an adrenaline-fueled adventure with thrilling car chases, explosive action and epic bosses! Race at high speed to the Decepticon bases, then convert into robot mode to blast your way to the boss!

name: Arctic Cat Snowmobile Racing
description: Become king of the mountain! Arctic Cat Extreme Snowmobile Racing allows players go on an epic snowmobile journey. Travel as far and fast as possible through endless scenic winter environments. Conquer hills, maneuver moguls, pound though powder, and clear mountain gaps. Upgrade real Arctic Cat sleds to catch big air and pull off sick tricks. Unleash your inner cat with customizable sled skins and characters.

name: SpaceGlider: Race For Time
description: Can you help Jori the Alien have the best time in Space's greatest race track? Based off a child favorite and one of video games most challenging levels the turbo tunnel, Space Glider gives you that same feeling but with our own twist.

name: Kart Stars
description: Welcome to the World Karting Championships! Race through a single player campaign or go head to head with players from around the world. Feel the rush as you play through vintage, sprint and super karts in a massive 300 round world championship season. Outrun the competition and finish on the podium to earn coins, upgrade your kart, and become the World Karting Champion!

name: Hot Donut
description: You are a high velocity donut in a beautiful world of hills. But there is water between you and escape. You must ROLL, JUMP, and DASH your way to freedom.

name: At Last not Last
description:
There is a very special forest. You wouldn't believe how many out-of-the-way things have happened there recently. For one, animals started racing to see who is the fastest. Maybe running from foxes is just too boring for them, I don't know.
I won't even start about the gigantic mushrooms that have sprung up after the last drizzle. And those massive holes in the ground! I dread to think of a creature that made those.

name: Fall Down! Deluxe
description: This is a simple but fast-paced and addictive game. Just touch screen to control the ball. Fall down through the holes and avoid the dead line. As time passed, the dead line will run faster and faster. The further you falling down the more your score. Collect the crystals to unlock extra playable characters and backgrounds. The farther you falling down the more crystals you will get.

name: Gogogo!
description: Gogogo! is a tournament-style party game for 3 to 16 players. There's a completely different challenge every round! There are memory challenges, reaction challenges, creative challenges, physical challenges and more. This is a chance to test your natural ability against your friends and family!

Can you and your team emerge triumphant and restore peace to the realm?

name: Pigskin Punter!
description: Cute and silly arcade game about punting pigskins! Indie developer looking for feedback! Can you beat the game?

name: Mr. Luma's Cooking Adventure
description:
Are you ready to go on a cooking adventure?
In Mr. Luma’s Cooking Adventure life is wonderful and relaxing. Explore a fairy-tale forest for all the ingredients nature has to offer, whether it’s delicious fruit, healthy vegetables or fresh fish. When your basket is full of goodies head back to your cozy tree house to cook for your furry little friends!
Let your imagination run wild in your fully equipped tree house kitchen! Slice, juice, fry and boil your ingredients. Once your plate is deliciously decorated, sit back and watch the adorable animals’ reactions.

name: Marshmallow 2x2
description:
Marshmallow 2x2 is a new number crunching game you have never played.
Are you ready for an unprecedented game play that will guarantee you will be addicted to it for the first time you play? Marshmallow 2X2 can do it! Please make sure you have enough time before you get it started!

name: Push Push Cat
description:
Push the blocks and make a way to save the cute cats who have lost their homes!!
Push Push Cat is a classic sliding puzzle game that anyone can easily learn and enjoy.
You can adopt cute homeless cats in various themes and customize them and shoot selfies.

You can meet many famous cats from around the world to empathize and heal.
Cats who are more affectionate than their stomachs, please come and pet them now!

name: Final 5: Survival!
description: Final 5 is a fast-paced, fun shooter, melee, time survival, adventure, action RPG game with roguelike elements. There’s no place else to run or hide, survival is your only goal.

name: Pompom: The Great Space Rescue
description: In a whole new kind of puzzle-action platformer, you do not control Pompom the hamster, but instead use your quick thinking to help him by placing and controlling platforms, obstacles and items around him. Analyze and use everything that comes your way: build bridges, place springs, prune vines... Be clever, be quick, be efficient. Travel through outer space to beaches full of flying fish, to ancient temples lost in the jungle, as you help Pompom outsmart his enemies and rescue his boy Hoshi from Captain Cat and his crew.

name: Speed Legends
description: Speed Legends takes the mobile racing & car driving genre to a whole new level by adding an addictive career mode, a gigantic open world, unlimited car tuning, stunning graphics and the most realistic car physics ever on mobile.

name: Xtreme Garage: Drifter
description: Xtreme Garage: Drifter is a 3D car racing game for drift and motorsport enthusiasts.

name: Data Link: Cyberpunk Racing
description: Data Link is an adventure arcade game with storyline made in the cyberpunk style like data wing.

name: Duck Dynasty: Battle of the Beards
description:
Battle of the Beards tests your reflexes and drops you “boots-first” into the Louisiana backwoods to compete in the Robertson family’s favorite redneck activities. Master rapid-fire challenges, unlocking gear and earning experience along the way, to prove you’ve got what it takes to grow a beard as long as your favorite Duckmen.   As you play, your character will go from a Bluetooth-earpiece-wearing, clean-shaven businessman, to a fully camouflaged, long-haired, bandana-clad backwoodsman with a beard that would even make Phil jealous.  
Can you keep up as the pace increases? Or will you be left in the dust as the heat turns up?

name: R.P.G
description:
Let's play rollcake playing game!
Drop rollcakes and delete them all!

name: Gophy
description: Run underground as a mischievous gopher, taking lawnmowers, flowers and mushrooms! Watch out though, the neighborhood doesn't like you! Watch out for giant spikes and fast cars! While you're running through, collect coins and redeem them in the Gophy Store for exciting new items!

name: Cube Cube!
description:
A beautiful, minimalistic runner game with lots of challenges and endless fun.
Only 1% can escape through level 10! Are you up for the challenge?

name: Mad Crash Racing
description: Avoid the accident with your beautiful red sport car. Do not drive the wrong way of the road. Tap to change the lane.

name: Rogue Racing: PinkSlip
description:
Street Racing. Custom Cars. Rogue Attitude
Get ready for a 100% personalized mobile racing experience! Create the ultimate, custom racing rig with over 50 different aftermarket parts and style options.Competie in pulse-pounding, winner-take-all events on gritty, inner-city streets.

name: Yo! Ninjia
description: Run, jump and shoot. This is a new type of action game with unique and impressive game experiences you have ever met.

name: Pixel Drifters
description: Get in the driver's seat and drift your way around a variety of obstacles and tight corners. Collect coins, earn combos, complete missions, and unlock the entire fleet of Pixel Drifters!

name: Metallicars
description: Metallicars is a new way of racing where intelligence rules over ability.

name: Karate Hero
description:
Karate Hero – Become a real karate master!
You can now become a true, black-belt karate master! Be a shocking maiden or a fiery dude! Fight, train and go through the single-player adventure. With 7 exciting martial-arts challenges, you will never be bored and quickly on your way to become a true hero of karate!

name: Two Hoops
description: Shoot some hoops. If one is fun two are funner. Super simple to play, yet very challenging. Try it now, the more you practice the better you get.

name: American Basketball: Guns & Balls
description: This ain't just basketball... this here's American Basketball! Yeehaw!

name: Football Penalty
description:
In the entertaining "Football Penalty" app, you, in turn represent itself as direct and the goalkeeper.
In the app simple and intuitively clear management.
In the menu choose quantity of shots on goal and tap "Play". When you the forward, concern a gate corner to which send a ball. When you the goalkeeper, concern a gate corner in which catch a ball.
Check the intuition. Foresee the direction of a jump of the goalkeeper or kick of the forward.
In the menu you can choose quantity of shots on goal from 5 to 50.
In each series of shots on goal the best and last results remain.
Score the maximum quantity of the goals at the minimum quantity of missed goals.
Good luck!

name: Shiodome Train Simulator
description: A realistic fictional railcar driving game is now available! Please enjoy driving on the various types of lines, over 70 km long, multiple tracks, tunnels, and various scenery changes. Single-track sections and many other types of trains are scheduled to be available in the future.

name: Tennis Online Duel
description: Online Tennis Duel is a realistic first person tennis game with an ideal physical ball. Play with your friends or someone random across the internet.

description: Package Dudes is a fast-paced local co-op game in which you play the role of a package sorting employees. Playing on your own or in teams, you'll struggle with a never-slowing conveyor belt, on which packages arrive. Sort them correctly and fight for the title of employee of the day!

description: Race through rainforests and beaches with motorcycles to navigate the winding paths while attempting to carry an egg! Time-trial your way to the top of the leaderboards, find and collect hidden treasures and artifacts, and do your best not to break an egg!

name: LightFall
description: A spirit that lived high in the sky falls to an underground city where gravity is randomly reversed for some reason. It's a 2D flat-former game where you have to explore the underworld and find a way to climb up to get back to where you were.

name: Chess Defense Saga
description: A chess-themed tower defense game with unique strategies, stories, and illustrations!

name: House of the Soul
description: Begin a journey of deception and discovery in 'HOUSE OF THE SOUL', a first-person exploration and story based experience. Explore an isolated mansion and descend into its lower levels as you discover the hidden secret project of the obsessive inventor who lives there.

name: Extreme Car Drift Simulator
description: If you want to drift wildly, this game is for you. With the drift game, you can have a great car driving simulation experience.

name: Mutant Fighting Cup
description:
Unlock, combine and splice your way to victory using your genetically engineered pet.
Raise him to be the greatest fighter the world has ever seen and battle it out over 5 continents.

Hone your skills in Europe, South America, Africa, Asia and North America before entering the World Cup for immortal glory.

Do you have what it takes to defeat all of the mutant fighter competitors?

name: Pylon Town
description: Western Power Distribution provides power to 7.9 million customers in the Midlands, the South West and South Wales. This new ‘Pylon Town’ app includes 7 brand new games that are aimed at delivering knowledge, safety and attitudes towards electricity.

name: Buddy, No!
description:
Buddy, the cute English bulldog who belongs to a world renowned inventor, is about to embark on a fast paced adventure like no other! His master recently invented a contraption that can create an unlimited supply of food for free! This one invention could literally change the world forever. It’s time to take it for a test drive in “Buddy, No!”

Get ready for an intense arcade-style game that will have you hooked from the very beginning! “Buddy, No!” is inspired by old-school handheld games that will bring high intensity mixed with a nostalgic feel. As the inventor’s machine begins to produce delicious food, Buddy licks his lips in anticipation! Burgers, ice cream, fries, and more fall from the machine and Buddy is happily waiting to gobble up the falling goodies. Watch out for the harmful objects that fall as well! Dodge the bad, feed on the good, and satisfy the hungry bulldog’s appetite! Yummy!

name: Crystal Lines
description: Crystal Lines is the most classic and amazing board game featuring addictive gameplay and tons of exciting new balls and power ups! Once you play , you can't stop!

name: Dragon Defender: Castle Kingdom Quest
description: Dragons are invading! They are destroying the village and threaten your castle! Defend it with your magic bow! Watch out for ogres and villagers running for help! Will your kingdom survive?

name: Mahjong Aztecs Mysteries
description:
Reveal the ancient mystery. Uncover secret of the Aztecs. Get ready to face the adventure of pyramids. This game will reveal your true skills. Play like a pro!
Mahjong is an ancient game that originated in China. It is a game of skill, intelligence, calculation and luck.
The aim is to clear up the board of stones and not to bring down the whole pyramid! The quicker you clear the pyramid the more points you'll get. Good Luck!

name: Slingo Adventure
description:
Get ready to play the latest release from everyone's favorite puzzle franchise, Slingo!
Join The Joker, The Cherub, and other classic Slingo characters on a bingo quest through the world of Fair Chance! It’s up to you to recover King Diamond’s stolen scepter and rescue the Queen from everyone’s favorite Slingo nemesis, The Devil.
Slingo Adventure combines classic slot machine gameplay with Bingo and Keno style number matching. Play through over 1000 (and counting) fun, fast paced levels by spinning, daubing, and wagering your way to success. Don’t forget! The faster you match, the bigger the bonus!

Use Power Ups to overcome challenges! Invite your friends via Facebook and keep track on each other’s progress and scores! Enjoy a variety of skill and chance minigames that let you wager your score! Newly added is the Collapse mode where you must clear the board within a set time! This is Slingo like you’ve never seen before!

name: Arena of the Mad King
description: Arena of the Mad King (AotMK) is a fast-paced bullet-hell boss rush game. Touhou meets Realm of the Mad God.

description: Builder. Designer. Renovator. Unleash your creativity in over a dozen unique places, get the right equipment, prepare the space, use what you find. Wanna make a crazy party?

name: Mighty Morphin Power Rangers
description: Mighty Morphin Power Rangers is an unreleased game for the Virtual Boy that appeared briefly on Nintendo Power’s Release Forecast lists in December 1995 and January 1996 with a release date of “Winter ’96”.

name: J.League 3D Stadium
description: J.League 3D Stadium is an unreleased soccer game for the Virtual Boy from J-Wing. It was slated for release in Japan on March 20th, 1996, but was ultimately cancelled when the Virtual Boy was discontinued. Not much is known about the game, as the only ever mention of it was when it was announced at Space World ’95.

name: Invincible Iron Man Gagaga-In
description:
Invincible Iron Man Gagaga-In is a cancelled “80’s giant robot fighting action game” for the Virtual Boy, that had been in development by Hudson Soft and the planning and contract development group Eighting. It was planned to release in Japan roughly a year after the system launch.

The game has never been officially announced, but images of a design document and an EP-ROM cartridge containing a sample build have been shared in 2018 by a former Hudson employee.

name: Intercept
description: Intercept is a cancelled game for the Virtual Boy

name: Genjin Show: Tobidase! VB Genjin
description: Genjin Show: Tobidase! VB Genjin is a cancelled game for the Virtual Boy.

name: Galaxian3
description: A cancelled Virtual Boy port of Galaxian 3.

name: Donkey Kong Country
description:
The developers at Rare intended to develop a Donkey Kong Country game for the Virtual Boy, but it was cancelled. The development went only as far as simple platforming stage which was made using Donkey Kong Land's graphics and rat enemies from Battletoads.

It was previously misremembered by a developer to be an early version of Donkey Kong Country 2: Diddy's Kong Quest.

No real footage of the game was ever found, with mock-ups being found on the internet.

name: Air Soccer Impossible
description: Sin descripción

name: AlphaSwap
description:
Alphaswap is a original word game that combines the elements of a Spelling Game Meets Word Search into a fast paced game for one to thousands of players!
Play vs. The World - Single players can play against other single players in a massive game where everyone is getting the same board/letters.

name: Angry World War 2

name: Atomic Pursuit
description:
A nuclear war aproaches, the entire planet is in serious danger. The last hope of the mankind is the space.
Some countries are sending their first missions looking for a new planet to colonize.
Choose your side, try to go the far as you can and became a national hero.
Be careful, your travel will be plenty of dangers. Keep an eye on the oxygen levels of your spaceship and take care of asteroids, they´ll be your worst enemy.

name: Best Word
description:
Best word is a turn-based word game played online with your friends and opponents all over the world.
It takes 30 seconds to learn, but 30 years to master!
The question is, do you have an enough prominent linguistic repertoire to shine, to win, to secure a place on the leaderboard?

name: Cosmic Quandary
description:
Your goal in Cosmic Quandary is simple -- move the wizards so their spell paths avoid each other and obstacles on the board!
Puzzles are randomly generated so you'll never run out of unique challenges each time you play!
Play through 40 levels in Puzzle Mode to unlock new wizards, obstacles, enemies, game modes, and more! When you're ready, try your luck in Timed Mode to see how many puzzles you can complete before time runs out!

name: Cubinko
description:
Your puzzle skills will be put to the test with this new match 3 game mode! Our exclusive ink blocks will expand your mind in ways you never imagined in this addictive puzzle game. Enjoy the satisfaction of fitting pieces perfectly into place, filling the board with an explosion of colors, and with an extremely fun design!
Are you ready to push your limits?

name: Dawn in the Air
description:
Become a Grand Master capturing ornithopters.
You have no idea which are the ornithopters?

name: Ice Cream Mania
description:
Embark on a flavorful adventure with Ice Cream Mania!
Compete with gamers from around the world or enjoy single-player mode!
Line up and move 3 matching ice creams to clear the level and win.
Experience over 390 exciting stages and share your top score.

name: Linum
description: Linum is a puzzle type game in which your goal is to Land Nodes on the Landing Points.

name: MicroSoccer
description: MicroSoccer is a fun and challenging retro style football game.

name: FleetMaster
description: Batthe and sink your opponent's ships before they can sink yours! Fast paced single and multiplayer action with leaderboards and achievements powered by GameCenter.

name: En Passant
description: En Passant is a light, clean and quite delightful chess game specifically designed to feel right at home on your gorgeous device. It offers a unique analyze mode, chess notations, themes, mood sharing, friendly sounds and stylish design.

name: Endless Mountain
description: Minimalist and intuitive controls: Tilt the phone to the left to turn left. Tilt the phone to the right to turn right. You don’t need to press any buttons! Really simple to play but giving you some really immersive sensations. This is not just another snowboarding game.

name: DuoDuo
description: Just tilt your device to control the DuoDuo. Fall down through the holes and avoid getting squished at the top. Get scores by staying alive as long as possible.

name: Swing Home Run

name: Roto16
description: Roto16 is a 21st century update to the age old 15 puzzle. Rather than shifting pieces to an empty spot, instead choose a corner where 4 tiles meet and rotate around that point.

name: Slide Golf Mini
description: Are you ready for an incredible Mini Golf game? Slide Golf Mini is a 1-2 player golf game that offers two 18 hole courses a 19th hole versus mode and a Golf Shop with new balls and backgrounds. There is now a reward system for a hole in one and course scores. Can you set a course record?

name: Smurfs' Village
description: The evil wizard Gargamel and his ever present cat companion, Azrael, have finally found the Smurfs’ village and have scattered our lovable blue friends far and wide throughout the enchanted forest. Come along with familiar friends, like Papa Smurf, Smurfette, Brainy, Jokey, Greedy and the rest of the Smurf family, as they guide you on a family fun adventure to build a new forest village for the Smurfs to call home.

name: Switchboard
description: Spell, lock, adapt and outduel. Switchboard is a brand new word game that combines turn-based word play with a healthy dose of strategy and a little bit of luck.

name: The Hacker 2.0
description:
The Hacker 2.0 is a turn-based strategy and puzzle hacking game set in a stylized virtual reality.
You'll use different hacking functions to complete missions in a clever way.

name: Train Your Brain
description: Train Your Brain is a game that requires high concentration.

name: Unravel Lines Puzzle
description: Unravel all lines by moving the balls across the board! Level is completed, when no lines are intersected. Every level has one more ball or one more connection, which makes the game progressively harder. Use your imagination and concentration and unravel every single line!

name: Zen Games: Color Blocks Puzzle
description:
Color Block Puzzle by Zen Games is a simple puzzle game for phones and tablets. This game has been built for stress relief. No rush, no hurry - a simple color blocks puzzle with no score or time limit. In this version of Zen games we have added 100 levels from easy to difficult. The game can be played by all ages by just moving the multi color blocks to match adjacent color and find your Zen.
Color Block Puzzle will improve your logic, coordination and help you relax with a soothing music as you cross each level moving color blocks and matching them. We have designed this zen game with soothing colours and happy music with a thought of helping you unwind.

name: Castle Rush
description:
You are having war as your neighboring country has been stealing things from your motherland.
You have to slide, drop and create box sets to fill up your inventory, show your power and make the enemy's army to change sides and win this battle!

name: Efpiyes
description: Efpiyes is a multiplayer first-person shooter with a built-in map editor that anyone can use.

name: Fliese
description: "Fliese" is a minimal logic puzzle game

name: NeuroSquad
description: Invent your own weapons in this sci-fi Roguelike shooter! Combine any weapon with any upgrade to customize your arsenal. Form a squad of holographic soldiers, redesign their guns too, and slay hordes of cybernetic enemies!

name: What if Adventure Time was a 3D Anime
description: What if Adventure Time was a 3D Anime is a third person action adventure fan game, developed by Mike Inel.

name: Price for Freedom: Avarice
description: Is an erotic cRPG set in the shared Price for Freedom universe. Enter our world in the role of Redic, a man looking to move on from his past and start a new life in the free trade city of Kaldea.

name: Astroneer: Jet Powered
description: The Jet Powered Update contains new vehicles to speed up Astroneer’s traversal of land and air! Use the new Hoverboard to shred planet surfaces while your friends use the VTOL to scout from the lower atmosphere!

name: Astroneer: Xenobiology
description: The Xenobiology Update features a new adventure where players embark on a narrative-focused mission across the solar system to discover the secrets behind the curious Galastropods.

name: Astroneer: Rails
description: EXO Dynamics is proud to introduce the brand new Rails System! The Rails System brings a new mode of transportation to Astroneer that excels at efficiency and convenience. Place rail posts to build out your rail lines, and then board the new railway vehicles for a hands-free transit experience. And unlike other vehicles, railway vehicles can travel autonomously, perfect for extending the reach of your automation network. But that’s not all: rail lines themselves carry both oxygen and power, making them an excellent way to connect together distant bases and excavation sites like never before!

name: Astroneer: Awakening
description:
Hello. I wanted to be sure you saw this. We will talk soon. Please pay attention when we meet. The task I have for you is very important.

You must finish all other priority missions beforehand. I will find you when you are ready. Do not worry. You will know when it is time.

name: Connection Error
description: Amber, an employee at GlobalNet Solutions, does her every-day night shift job in the IT Department, most of it being in the server room. Though somebody is stalking inside the darkness...

name: Abandoned Drive-in
description: The main character Kaori is on a date boyfriend suggests that they go on a test of courage. The destination is an abandoned drive-in. They hear a noise in the ruins and stops. Is there already someone there?

name: Tennis Manager Mobile
description: Tennis Manager is back for the 2023 season with an updated tennis world tour and new goals and achievements! Become the best tennis manager ever! Build your own tennis academy, find the next tennis super stars and make your team of pro players climb the worldwide ranking. A game inspired by Patrick Mouratoglou, coach of Serena Williams!

name: Running Rich Racing
description: Sin descripción

name: Jumanji: Epic Run
description:
Welcome to Jumanji!
Once again, Jumanji is in peril. The sacred Falcon Jewel has been stolen, and it’s up to you to recover it.

Run from howling hyenas, climb mountains, avoid avalanches, free fall from deadly waterfalls, and defeat anyone in your way.
Avoid dangerous animals from the game, including rhinos, vultures, jaguars, and more ... watch out at all times!

name: A Blocky Kind of Love
description: A fresh new take on a love adventure lets you pursue romance on a wild ride over land sea and air. Your object of affection needs to be won over. Do you have what it takes to win her/his heart?

name: Byte Rider
description: Introducing a dystopian, cyberpunk future of brave data-hackers, breakneck excitement, and breathtaking graphics…. Welcome to Byte Rider! Dodge and his sister Weave have hacked their way into a honeypot of data that threatens to be their last! Only you can save them from gun-toting hover-drones, vicious vehicles, and the surreal streets of Cyber City. Blaze your byte-cycle through a maze of madness, collect your data, and hack your way through this mind-bending adventure!

name: Hobo: Life Business Simulator
description: The game allows you to live your virtual life started as an unknown hobo, achieve fame and even become a president of your country! One action in the game takes 1 game day. Every day your mood, health and satiety decreases. If the level of vital signs falls to zero, you’ll have 7 days to raise it, otherwise you will die. Return bottles, gain money!

name: Nitro Rally Evolution
description: "Nitro Rally Evolution" is totally inspired by the old classic arcade racing games of the 80's; great gameplay and perfect cars control system makes the game as the first 100% arcade rally racing game on your iOS Device!

name: Kaepernick Football
description: Play as the clutch QB on the game-winning drive. Pass or run, every play counts with 60 seconds left. Can you make the big-time quarterback throws for the 4th QTR comeback?

name: Virtual Bomberman
description: Virtual Bomberman is a cancelled game in the Bomberman series that was planned to be released for the Virtual Boy. It was scheduled to be released in February 29th 1996.

name: Order's Up
description: Take control of the counter and serve food to all of the hungry customers! Make sure to complete their order in time, and in the correct sequence or risk ruining their meal. Earn cash to purchase new restaurants and increase your earning potential.

name: Herd!!!
description:
In your farm, there are lots of livestock.Believe that these cute animals have not enough intelligence back to their nests, you can guide them find the right path to return their home, at the same time, please be careful wolf coming.
How many animals can you guide ?

name: Mr Octopus
description: Sin descripción

description:
"Wedding run" is simple but new type running game.
(Actually it isn't as easy as that...very hard.)

name: Jippo! Street
description: Building a street has never been this fun and easy! Just swipe and match falling dice to create new buildings for the funny Jippo characters!

description:
To survive In the deep, dark space, the fireflies must always reach out for the light! But it it’s not an easy task - lots of obstacles and enemies are in the way.

Alien warlords called the Q’Tath have decimated earth’s defenses.
As they spread across the galaxy, their rations ran low…
So they rounded up and imprisoned the people of Earth.
Now, the fate of the world rests on your shoulders.
Repel the Q’Tath from 5 new battlegrounds.
Free the prisoners.
Save humanity!

When all the ingredients are used up, the players discover which burgers were maked properly, and which were not. The players take back their orders for their improperly maked burgers so they can try again in the next round. After three rounds, the player who has delivered the most burgers is the best burger maker and the winner!

Build your cars, create new ones, make your workers happy, please your customers, arrange your retail stores and play with your friends.

name: Brazen Fruit
description:
Let's go Brazen Fruit! Make combos by combining colorful fruits!
Start playing Brazen Fruit
This unique game is one of the most interesting mobile games of all time!
Match Fruits in this combo arcade game to progress to the next level.
Get that great feeling when your best combos rewarded with gold keys and other bonuses!
Take on this great game alone or play with friends to see who can finished all levels!
Brazen Fruit is completely free to play.
Get ready for a fun new adventures with Brazen Fruit!

name: NASCAR Manager
description: NASCAR Manager is the all new official NASCAR game that puts you in control! Take the Crew Chief seat in the most popular motorsport in North America. Decide your strategy, run the best tactics and make the calls that guide your driver to victory! Are you ready for a real challenge?

name: With My Cat

Spend more time with your kittens and get to know them.
Various kinds and personalities. Let's start a new life with unique kittens.

name: LightEaters!
description:
The LightEaters are coming… because darkness is never safe! Explore the perils and pitfalls of the night with the help of your trusty flashlight in this whimsically spooky platform adventure game.

The mysterious LightEaters aren’t the only dangers lurking in the murk! You’ll need wits, speed, and the power of your imagination to navigate through the dark, defeat traps and puzzles, and evade the enemies in your way!

name: Jelly Cube Blast
description:
Dive into a new thrilling puzzle challenge!
Help Flan and Soufflé in their exciting adventure to save their grandma, Baba Praline. They will need all of your brains and BLASTS to destroy every Jelly Cube in each level! Solve the colorful puzzle levels to help them during their journey!

name: Blocks Hurt!

Play with blocks in a way you never imagined!
Freaky creatures are coming for you… Stop them! Unchain your deadly blocks, match them, stack them or hurl them against this parade of bizarre monsters!
Are you ready for the most unconventional matching block experience!?

name: Dice Dreams
description:
Welcome to Dice Dreams!
Roll the dice on Dice dreams, build your magical kingdom and become the Dice King!
Start your board game adventure and join your friends in this dice quest.
With every roll of the dice, you can earn free coins and expand your kingdom. Every dice roll starts a new dice adventure filled with fun and excitement!

name: Brwanjeya
description:
Brwanjeya: is a free-to-play mobile match-three puzzle game. Players compete to stay on the game board by swapping black and white pieces on the board to make a match of three points on the same straight line. It’s a challenging game that motivates you to compete with your competitors.
Take on this amazing adventure alone or play with friends to see who can get the top score!

name: Vacation Adventures: Park Ranger 13 - Collector's Edition
description: Help run Pinecreek Hills and New England's Minuteman Valley!

name: Hiden Ruin
description: A challenging platform game that will test your skill and patience.

name: Balance Helicopter
description: Balance the helicopter with its two engines! Navigate through increasingly harder levels and different challenges!

name: Idlenetics
description: Exciting idle tycoon game that immerses you in a beautiful medieval world. The game features a hex-based map that is divided into different zones, each of which is unlocked as the player progresses through the game.

name: TVs: The Revival
description: TVs The Revival is a platformer single-player game that balances exciting action with challenging puzzles. When the hero "u" awakens from a coma, he is driven through strange events living in the TVs real world to unravel the mysteries of his past and defeat evil forces plaguing the region.

name: Backroom Warfare II
description: Fight for survival in the Backrooms. Play with friends in multiplayer or solo against AI bots. Unearth the terrifying monster scorestreak and get ready for an intense experience!

name: How to Die: A Hope Beneath
description: A box was trapped inside a mysterious chamber. There's no way escape from there, except... death. How to Die is a dark, narrative-driven 3D platformer with lot of challenging puzzles.

name: Lido: The Puzzle Hero
description:
Lido is a hero of the addicting brain teaser – a block puzzle game that will challenge you and train your brain. Put your puzzle skills to the test – we dare you to reach the highest score! A relaxing and easy-to-learn match 3 puzzle game to keep you playing for hours on end! Drag & drop puzzle pieces on the board, aiming to combine sets of 3 or more of the same color. Merge three to clear the puzzle blocks, leaving space for new pieces. The more you clear at once, the higher your score will be.
How many colorful blocks can you connect?

name: Nine Tiles
description:
Welcome to NineTiles: The anagram puzzle game that challenges your vocabulary and the speed of your wits.
Battle against the clock to create as many words as you can in survival mode or take a relaxed approach and test your word knowledge with clues and without time pressure in the main game mode. Compete with friends to see who can get to the top of the leaderboards and be the sharpest tile in the box.

name: Blocki!
description:
Blocki! is a unique game you haven't seen before. Guide a bird on the board to collect all the scattered pieces and create the displayed shape. Evaluate your logical thinking ability, reflexes, accuracy and creativity. If you're up for a brand new brain teaser you found the right place.
Test your intuition and explore beautifully hand crafted puzzle levels!

name: One Block: Puzzle Adventure
description:
Do you like puzzles games or brain teasers? You are in a right place!
 One Block is a logic game which focuses on thinking and solving skills. Each puzzle makes you think few steps ahead and gets more and more challenging as you progress.
Hand crafted levels filled with various innovative mechanics are ready to be solved. The goal is simple: merge blocks of the same color and collect stars simultaneously. By the way, you have to stay in the board frame! The logic puzzle starts simple but further in the game you will encounter new elements. Take advantage of each game element and use their powers to stay on the board in order to complete a level.

name: Dead Space: Strange Transmissions Quest Pack
description: Isaac Clarke has landed on the Island with the survival skills needed. Includes 1 Outfit, 2 Back Blings, 1 Pickaxe, 1 Built-In Emote and Quests to earn up to 1,500 V-Bucks.

Ohka Bots is a free-to-play action role-playing multiplayer online game available for PC.

A battle to save Cyberspace and become the strongest BOT you can be. Upgrade and customize your BOT as you power up and loot your way through the Virus threat that has infested Cyberspace.

name: Astrobit
description: A free PvP space shooter with epic RPG mechanics. Upgrade your ship and explore new builds every match by combining different weapons, skills and abilities. Be a swift assassin, a tanky heavy-hitter, or go deep into magic to destroy your opponent and climb the ranks. The choice is yours!

name: Outlaw Heart
description:
Outlaw Heart is a Fast Paced Character Action/Rail Shooter that is playable on Flatscreen or VR!

Help Remy and her band shred their way through the city they love!

name: Madshot: Road to Madness
description:
Road to Madness is a stand-alone spin-off of Madshot, which introduce a new vertical-style survivor gameplay!
Slaughter endless abominations while moving stylishly through a lovecraftian nightmare. Combine a multitude of unlockable weapons, abilities and upgrades in order to survive as long as possible, and reach the top of the leaderboards.

name: Omega Survivors
description: Omega Survivor is a sci-fi bullet hell, part of the new "Survivor" genre with loot, crafting and lots of alien blasting to be done. The perfect game for those that just want to relax and turn off their brain.

name: SoundStorm
description: A Shoot 'em Up with music driven gameplay. Bullets flash to the rhythm of the music. Hit the bullets exactly on the beat to destroy them and make chain reactions. Feel the music and enjoy the unique game experience combining patterns and rhythms.

name: Tales of Shinobi
description: Tales of Shinobi is a single-player adventure game where you get to play as a powerful Shinobi who must save the world from evil!

name: Stick War 3

name: De Blob

name: Eggies
description:
Hatch the all Eggies!
Eggies want to be part of our planet but their eggs need great sense for solicitude and care. Are you good enough to feed, cure and hatch them all? Your reward will be love and fun gained from your virtual pets.
Eggies are ready to play with you various games like Flappy Egg, Pexeso, Puzzle. Visit shop where you can decorate your Eggie or change its appearance. Do you have favorite color? Or would you like to try some ornament or original hat? Everything is possible!

name: Eevoo II
description: Play eevoo and discover a new world! Professor McEvo has opened a portal to a parallel dimension directly atop our own. Your task is to enter the fantastical world of eevoo to aid him in his research. Settle a new and uncharted land, claim real world locations in a virtual world, build your own empire, challenge your friends, and experience the stunning Augmented Reality gameplay of this brave new world.

name: Buoy Boy
description:
The endless floater adventure of Buoy Boy is here!
Help him become a real boy again and collect all the treasure in the ocean.

name: Brain Battle
description:
Good old pen & paper game known from schooldays is now on mobile! That’s Brain Battle - Trivia and Word game.
Grab your knowledge of cars, animals, actors and actresses and many more categories and challenge up to three friends or random players to the showdown of brain power.

name: Monster Bang
description: Monster Bang is a classical Match 3 Game. Super fun! Easy to play. You just need to move the monsters to make 3 or more monsters of the same kind in one line and they will be crushed. Play more and more surprise!

name: Ninja Chicken 2
description: Ninja Chicken 2 is a very enjoyable, addictive game with a highly amusing and original premise and its great for short bursts or to play for ages.

name: Nitro Nation: Drag Racing
description: Race, mod, and tune dozens of real licensed cars. Start a team, invite your friends, win tournaments. Trade car parts with other racers in real time and build your dream car for both Drag and Drift races!

name: Paradise Story
description:
The schedule of an angel in paradise may not be quite what you expect…
You may think it is quiet… that there is nothing to do…
Think again ! There is no shortage of work to do in paradise ! To realise this, you will live a busy day beyond the clouds… Oh my God !

name: Pen Fight
description: Knock your opponent’s pens off the table by flicking your pen against theirs! Pen Fight is a fantastic new game that combines simple controls, great physics, and an element of strategy.

name: Quarter Monkey
description: Quarter Monkey or "Rob3 Erd", The well-known Egyptian traditional game revamped to suit all of us.

name: ReCharge RC
description: Drift your way into ReCharge RC! Featuring limitless vehicle customization, online track sharing with an ever growing catalog, global online leaderboards for every track, even the ones you create, and asynchronous multiplayer allowing you to race the ghost of every leaderboard entry! Enjoy realistic physics that blur the lines between arcade and simulation and allow rookies and veterans alike to experience the joy that is RC racing!

description: Sin descripción

name: SkyDive Racer
description:
Race through the sky as you glide and parachute from plane to ship. Pick up coins throughout different routes while avoiding drones, birds and other obstacles. Collect mystery boxes along the way to gain special abilities. Upgrade your player to improve your chance to be the best skydive racer.
Can you finish first? No matter what happens, dance with your friends at the end of each landing. Have fun!

name: Mini Racing: Mini Cars Curling
description:
Do you remember mini cars you played with your friends when you were child?
Very small, but very fast our mini car race.
The mini cars came back as game!

name: Mini Golf Halloween
description: Featuring 30 scary and challenging holes, fantastic graphics, accurate physics and a spooky atmosphere.

name: Math Genius King of Arithmetic
description: The best math gameplay! Have fun with Math Genius and prove that you are a prodigy of mathematics. Additions, subtractions or both, divisions and multiplications. With this app you can improve your mathematical calculation skills. Train and compete with friends. As a mathematics quiz you will have to indicate the result of each operation before it reaches the ground.

name: Jetrats Defense
description:
Jetrats Defense is an addictive defense game! It reached Top10 games in several countries.
Build some towers then wait your enemies pass through? No No No! Let's take up weapons and shoot them!
Don't deceiving by the first several simple levels, the following battles is really tough, that's why the simple levels are there!

name: GT Ride
description:
The Kia pro_cee'd GT presents GT RIDE. The racing app like no other.
Create tracks by moving your mobile device through the air. Race them and challenge your friends!
To create unique tracks of your own download the GT RIDE app to your smartphone or tablet. Start creating tracks by simply moving your mobile device around through the air. The in-built sensors will track your movements and turn them into 3D tracks with curves and loops that you'll never have experienced before!
Find out who's more skilled at racing – you or your friends?
Share your tracks and challenge them. Race theirs to break their record and get ahead of them in the highscore.

name: Hidden Garden Word Scramble
description: Enter the garden with a whole new objective! Hidden Garden Word Scramble is the first in a series of word based puzzle games in the Hidden Garden Series. Try to make as many words as you can with the letters given to you before time runs out!

name: High Dive
description:
Walter likes diving. Birds like flying. Hmmmmmmm.
Help Walter break the world outdoor diving record in this pseudo–endless arcade diver!

name: Icontrivia: Guess the Character
description:
Test your knowledge about these popular characters from cartoons, fairytales, movies and others, in this highly addictive word guessing game.
Hints & Help: Struggling to guess a character? You can reveal or remove letters to help you figure out the character.

name: Explo Bee
description:
Help the dizzy spinning bee fly from flower to flower pollinating as he goes!
Simply tap the screen to launch the bee and he will fly in a straight line (hopefully) landing on another flower. Go for Speed combos or play it safe, but make sure your aim is true or you will lose the bee.
Don't wait too much on a flower or you'll explode!!!
BuzzBee features an easy, pick up and play, one-touch control scheme. Suitable for any age, the game offers cute, colorful graphics and full-length musical scores.
There are ten rounds of gameplay which progressively increase in difficulty, local high score rankings and even a voice-over by a professional opera singer.

name: TouchSports Tennis 2012 HD
description: Tired of Tennis games with difficult controls that just don't work? Tennis 2012's Natural Motion controls allow players to effortlessly move on the court and play like a pro. Dragging one finger on the screen moves the tennis player. Swiping with 2 fingers swings the racket with ultimate precision and controls. Its that easy! Place a drop shot just over the net, out of your opponents reach, lob the ball over your opponent to back court, or smash a top spin cross court. A control system designed for pro players and beginners alike!

name: White Tiles Master
description: An addicting game that tests your reflexes against time and movement. Test your speed and accuracy with this simple and fun game!

name: Woodroid HD+
description: Woodroid mix the brick breaker gameplay, pixelart graphics and awesome visual effects to enjoy breaking all the pixels for free during more than 100 levels.

name: Word Search & Learn
description: It's time to WORD SEARCH & LEARN: The new FREE game from Mobnyx!!! A whole new experience in Word Search games: you will challenge your brain and learn at the same time!

name: Under the Sea: Swim
description:
This gams is big fun with tough , speed, exciting!
you have to escape from big fish!

name: Underworld Football Manager
description:
Underworld Football Manager 2019-2020 mixes traditional soccer club tactics and strategy with bribery and sabotage in a unique twist on soccer management.
Build a soccer empire and pit your top eleven players against millions of managers across the globe. Part football manager, part city builder, part strategy, you’ll need to sign young pro players and turn them into superstars, while building up your city and facilities to gain every inch of advantage you can.
But simply setting up your squad isn’t enough! You’ll need to use all your cunning to bribe and attack your opponents’ players, and vandalize their facilities to gain an edge over the competition!

name: Very Iconic Pixels - 80s Quiz
description:
Put your 80s knowledge to the test with the VIP 80s retro pixel quiz!
We’re taking you time-travelling in the DeLorean back to the world of 80s music, movies, TV and sport, where you’ll identify iconic pixel-art characters to score stars and progress along the Hollywood Walk of Fame.

name: Star Connect
description:
Something wakes Lucy up in the middle of the night. It's the stars! And they need help!
Join her in this trip connecting the stars and making them glow. All around the sky there are constellations to join but you will soon encounter difficulties such as satellites and black holes.

name: Soccer Wind Shot
description: You must kick the ball in the goal in this simple and addictive windy soccer game!

name: Soccer Showdown 3
description: Soccer Showdown's genre-revolutionizing PhysKick engine gives you perfect control over every kick. This isn't your average "flick-the-ball" soccer game. Soccer Showdown is entirely physics based; your finger IS your foot.

name: Zane
description:
What is Zane ?
Zane is harmony.
Absolute new logic game with unique game play and visual logic.
Everyone of 50 level has multiple beautiful solutions.
Find the balance of your inner Zane and reach harmony.

name: Oh! Sheep
description:
Command a group of wooly friends to save the world from the evil Dr.Friedrich in this fun and challenging path-drawing puzzle game!
Lead a herd of sheep by drawing paths to command them and get past obstacles.
Steal magic berries from the mad scientist to save the world. Use the berries to change color and trigger switches to help the sheep escape!

name: Laps Fuse: Puzzle with Numbers
description: Fuse your tiles together and play for hours with addicting puzzle mechanics in Laps!

name: The Lost Crown
description:
Return the crown to king's castle.
Challenge yourself with 3 stars.
Piece can only move on path with same color.

name: Totem Clash
description:
Totem Clash is a 2-player strategy game that excels on design.
The objective of the game is to push your opponent out of the board while trying to stay alive. To do so, you will have to protect capture points, collect items and find the best positioning.

name: Recon in Force
description: ReconInForce is a turn based strategy game using deception, ambush, and tactics. Dominate the field with an armada of troops and unlimited strategic options. Sneak through cities and forests or deploy smoke to hide until it is time to strike. Spy on the enemy with scouts to prevent surprises. Leverage the strengths of your commanders and soldiers to attack and destroy the enemy’s base!

name: Shuzle
description: Minimalistic mind-bending shuffle puzzle.

name: Aqua Jewel
description:
This is a puzzle game where you link three jewels to make them disappear within the time limit.
AquaJewel provides two modes for you; the Classic Mode where you can
level up gradually or the Quest Mode where you have to change all the
panel background to complete a level!

name: Black Eye Spin
description:
Black Eye Spin continues series of puzzle-multiplayer games.
Playing this game you have to spin the wheel and catch colored balls. 3 or more adjacent one color balls explode and create X balls. X balls create higher value X balls. Highest is black ball. We call it Black Eye. Wheel has only 16 slots. So it will be good exercise for your brain trying not to fill all the slots otherwise the game will end.
All created X balls will be collected and can be used in multiplayer game Black Eye World – another same series game.

name: Glow
description:
Glow is an extremely addictive puzzle game, and by far the best game of its kind in AppStore yet!
The Rule is simple: Light-up the shape with a continuous line without retracing paths!
The addictiveness of this game has been proven with several similar Chart-Topping Apps! But have you been frustrated with their improvement-needed controls, and the limited puzzle counts?

name: Gem Collapse
description: Fast paced block busting fun in this action packed game! Test your skill and reflexes as you race to complete the level before the blocks overpower you. Use awesome power-ups to help you along, and play through numerous levels as you try your hardest to master the game.

name: Trupuzzle
description:
Trupuzzle is a game for those who like racking their brains over passing seemingly a simple level. And then, having passed, you feel completely satisfied.
On the playing field of TRUpuzzlE there are groups of green pieces of several colors. The player’s task comes to moving the green group of pieces into a specified location. In fact, it’s not easy, you will have to make up multi-steps combinations trying to remove unnecessary pieces from you path.
Visually the game looks really attractive – it is developed in steam-punk style. TRUpuzzlE provides several dozens of levels and the application is universal.

name: Notakto
description:
Simple to learn and hard to master, Notakto is a variation on Tic-Tac-Toe where BOTH players make X's and whoever makes three-in-a-row loses.
Difficulty ranges from Easy to Insane. At Insane, the computer uses advanced game theory techniques to play a perfect game, so don't make any mistakes if you want to win!
Unlock all levels and play on up to six boards at the same time!
Choose Rated Play and work toward becoming Notakto World Champion.

name: Sudoku For 2
description: Introducing "Sudoku For 2"! Now you can play sudoku with friends, with family, or join random match games. Explore the whole new way of enjoying sudoku puzzle!

name: Pickle Pete
description:
A mysterious substance has turned Pete into a pickle!
Darkness has settled over the world, and our hero must find a way to survive against the waves of evil forces. Stack up, gear up, and create countless combinations of unique builds to become stronger than your enemies. Find the antidote and save the world!

name: Dungeon Time
description:
A sorcerer known as the Prophet has spilled Chaos into the world. Four weathered adventurers must track him down and find out if it was just a misunderstanding or if the world is really going to end.
Dungeon Time features arcade quality gaming with a sprinkle of smooth mobile controls. Crawl with up to 4 players Co-Op or go just go it alone. Homage to RPG & shmup classics - a top-down shooter with zombies, wizards, demons, and exploding owls.

name: Sniper Somali Strike
description: Capt. Tom Deom, 43, has been taken hostage by pirates who tried to hijack the U.S.-flagged Marsk Alabama. The Ventura county native is being held on a speed-boat that is heading towards Somalia's anarchic, gun-plagued shores.

name: Meteor Commander
description: Retro-inspired arcade-style shooter. Save humanity from incoming waves of flaming hot meteors, alien ships hell-bent on destroying humanity, and the strangeness of space by shooting, blasting and nuking incoming waves of meteors and enemies.

name: Metroid Dread
description:
Metroid Dread is a cancelled DS game for the Metroid series that was later reworked into the Nintendo Switch game of the same name. The game is notable for being in development hell, having been originally developed for the Nintendo DS. This early version of the game has never been publicly shown off.

This early version has the same basic premise as the final one, with Samus trapped on an alien world, trying to survive against an unstoppable foe. And as it's a sequel to Metroid Fusion, it presumably would have carried the plot point of Samus being on the run from the Galactic Federation.

No prototype builds or ROMs have ever surfaced for this DS version, and it is unlikely Nintendo will release any. It's a possibility that concept art or screenshots of this early version will be revealed in the upcoming art book, as Nintendo is open to talking about Metroid Dread's development history.

Liam Robertson of Unseen64 claims that a synopsis of the game was given out to select members of the press. And in 2010, IGN's Craig Harris said in a podcast that he had seen a complete script for Metroid Dread, and that "Nintendo could use it anytime they wanted." It's possible that this was the synopsis that Liam Robertson was referring to. After the 2021 announcement of the game, Harris was asked on Twitter if he remembered anything from this script. He said he didn't
